#: '''從'''[[今天]]'''起'''[[他]][[就]][[成為]][[總經理]][[了]] (''[[Traditional Chinese|trad.]]'')
#: '''Cóng''' jīntiān '''qǐ''' tā jiù chéngwéi zǒngjīnglǐ le
#: ''He became the general manager '''from''' today '''on'''''

